## How to Refresh Data

To pull fresh messages, use the Telegram MCP tool `telegram_get_messages` with:
- `chat`: "Unity Network - Verified"
- `limit`: up to 5000 per call
- `offset_date` / `min_date`: to specify date ranges

For large pulls, chunk by week to avoid the 5000 message limit on busy periods.
